Edit chuckwalla-conf.php and enter your database credentials.

Import dev/sql/schema.sql into the database.

Copy index.php-dist and ircbot.php-dist to non-"-dist" variants.

Edit your connection information in app/modules/Bot/config/connection.xml

Run ircbot.php from inside pub/

Call index.php in your browser. Currently not finished there, but try index.php/channel/%23channelname/live?since=1

